Simulate the impact of tax reforms on citizens. 

Powered by Etalab and part of the EIG program (General Interest Entrepreneur), the team works with admninistrator within the French National Assembly.

This project aims at helping administrators and deputees to simulate the impact of reforms on the government budget before its vote. 

LexImpact started in 2019 and is still in progress.

